{"id": "1359482947744436315", "channel_id": "1359482947744436315", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "大腦中斑斕的想像與記憶最是美味，為克萊門汀獻上你的腦洞，製作最獨一無二的表情包取悅她吧~\n特別的作品將獲得克萊門汀的額外獎賞——一次沉浸式的心靈診療，在顱內感受來自宇宙深處的蟲鳴！\n\n讓我們今夜一起變成克萊門汀的「蟲家人」🙏「蟲門」，萬歲！\n\n**▌活動說明：**圍繞克萊門汀製作專屬與她的表情包~素材來源可以是遊戲內克萊門汀的相關截圖、原創繪製的小表情……（注：真人照片、AI生成內容不在本次活動範圍內）\n**▌活動時間：** 2025年4月9日 - 2025年4月11日\n**▌活動獎勵：**獎勵會隨著留言區自製表情包的數量增加而持續加碼，基本獎勵為100銀芯\n（1）≥10條，抽3位守密人送出「100銀芯」；即3位守密人 皆獲得100銀芯\n（2）≥20條，追加3位守密人，銀芯加碼至「200銀芯」；即6位守密人 皆獲得200銀芯\n（3）≥30條，追加5位守密人，銀芯加碼至「300銀芯」；即11位守密人 皆獲得300銀芯\n\n後續會整理有趣的表情包作品展示分享，期待各位守密人的腦洞😼\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\n**【Rewarded interaction: An invitation from \"Cle🦋tine\"】**\n\n 🦋The colorful imagination and memory in the brain are the most delicious. Offer your imagination to Clementine and make the most unique emoticon package to please her~\n 🦋Special works will receive an extra reward from Clementine - an immersive spiritual diagnosis and treatment, where you can feel the sound of insects from the depths of the universe in your brain!\n\nLet's enjoy the chirping of insects tonight！\nWe will organize interesting emoji works for display later, and look forward to the imagination of all the secret keepers~😼\n\n**▌Please check the detailed activity rules in the comment area！**", "timestamp": "2025-04-09T10:59:52.714000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-04-10T07:11:00.529000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}], "attachments": [{"id": "1359482948025323671", "filename": "1.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 656736, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1359482947744436315/1359482948025323671/1.JPG?ex=69ccfaa8&is=69cba928&hm=6732d54b7a667c0c8c5d81bbf53e90ae5ea2940e8766a476d58898c4e0954296&"}, {"id": "1359482948436492479", "filename": "2.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 156762, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/135948294774