{"id": "1359483459256455179", "channel_id": "1359482947744436315", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "🦋  **【Interaction Rules】**\n**▌Interaction Instructions: **Create an exclusive emoticon pack for Clementine. The source of the material can be related screenshots of Clementine in the game, original emoticons...\n (Note: real photos and AI-generated content are invalid)\n**▌Interaction time:** April 9, 2025 - April 11, 2025\n**▌Interaction Rewards: **The rewards will increase with the number of self-made emoticons in the comment area, and the basic reward is 100 silver cores\n(1) If there are ≥10 items, three keepers will be selected to receive \"100 Silver Cores\"; that is, all three keepers will receive 100 Silver Cores.\n(2) If there are ≥20 items, add 3 more keepers and the silver core bonus will be increased to \"200 silver cores\", that is, all 6 keepers will receive 200 silver cores.\n(3) If there are ≥30 items, 5 additional keepers will be added, and the silver core bonus will be increased to \"300 silver cores\", that is, all 11 keepers will receive 300 silver cores.\n\n🦋  **【Reference Image】**\nLooking forward to your creations~", "timestamp": "2025-04-09T11:01:54.668000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-04-09T11:02:17.133000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1359483458577240215", "filename": "1.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 176997, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1359482947744436315/1359483458577240215/1.JPG?ex=69ccfb22&is=69cba9a2&hm=4d3b9d20a9f7db663e6845d8a1f5b9520450f10161646189a6e7044e8c597019&"}, {"id": "1359483458875031814", "filename": "2.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 147393, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1359482947744436315/1359483458875031814/2.JPG?ex=69ccfb22&is=69cba9a2&hm=ae465286917347a4c82048979ce4f627602f299bd4a4bcfdbd2a0c47e60b4a86&"}, {"id": "13594834591